    "title": "Opening for Production Engineer at Astral Pipes Ventures Solutions",
    "description": "We at Astral Pipes Ventures Solutions are looking for an experienced Production Engineer based out of Chennai. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Astral Pipes Ventures Solutions:\nAstral Pipes Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in FMEA\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Referral bonus program\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Astral Pipes Ventures Solutions!",
